*German: [[Kern]] ''m'' (1), [[Grube]] ''f'' (2), [[Box]] ''f'' (3)

====Related words====

* [[pit stop]] (3)

=== Verb ===
'''to pit'''
# To oppose, as in "to pit one's wits against someone".

